Evolutionary solver is important because it garuantees a correct answer, howerver the downside is that it may take a very long time for solver to come up with the optimal solution.  It also may come up with more than one optimal solution.  It also can solve for non-linear problems better than normal solver.  Regular solver has a difficlult time with non-linear problems.  However, evolutionary solver can figure out the optimal solution.
